    "en": {
      "title": "CCPI inflation climbs to 60.8%",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Colombo Consumer Price Index (CCPI) inflation climbed to 60.8% Y-o-y in July 2022, while the CCPI inflation grew by 4.5% in July, in contrast with June 2022.",
        "Inflation climbed primarily due to transport, restaurants and hotels, fish, rice and utilities.",
        "Food inflation increased 90.9% while non food inflation increased 46.5% YoY.",
        "Significantly, the largest montly increase has been recorded in the transport sector, from 128% in June to 143.6% in July."
      ],
